{"tid":995090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曾與 LIHKG 和達哥合作過推出角色的《戰月勇者》宣布結束營運！","createTime":"2019-01-25T07:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T08:08:11.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4557fb2121cf77c0b43cb9f44427a25671d3817","tid":995090,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"突然出公告，或許大家都已經猜到，《戰月勇者》終於走到盡頭了。小編想了好久，也不知應該如何告訴大家，應該如何出這公告。與其說《戰月勇者》陪伴了大家 4 年，不如說大家陪了小編 4 年。<br />\n<br />\n小編不敢說我們是個成功的遊戲，但我們也和大家一起歡笑過，也希望可以為大家帶來一個有趣的遊戲。可惜最終讓大家失望了。這段時間我們經歷了很多，也學到很多。最讓小編難忘的不是駭客事件（雖然也真的足夠難忘了），而是親身直播，直接和各位玩家互動溝通。小編當時真的很緊張，也很怕大家會對小編失望或者說錯話。但也看到很多人支持我們和鼓勵我們。小編也一直很自豪可以和大家分享。我還很記得有玩家和我們分享他的家庭旅行照片、工作的事、遊戲的意見、對我們的提點，還有調笑小編。<br />\n<br />\n　　雖然我們一直堅持、萬般不捨，但是現在已到不得不別離的時候了。《戰月勇者》將會於 2019 年 2 月 8 日晚上 11 時 59 分正式停止營運，並於 GOOGLE STORE 及 APP STORE 下架。所以這段時間大家就不要課金啦，想要甚麼跟小編說一聲就是了^^。多謝大家一直以來的支持，如有問題可以聯絡小編。小編相信我們還會再見的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/805161479551830/posts/2036930066374959/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F805161479551830%2Fposts%2F2036930066374959%2F&d=1JqvwWNHjQPDp8tWt%2FwICi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=de1d6593\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/805161479551830/posts/2036930066374959/</a>"},{"pid":"c93b47ddf9e90ab91881933e1900bc4737a8b194","tid":995090,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">昔日資訊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[突發] 連尼住同《戰月勇者》合作！推出LIHKG扭蛋活動？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/275653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/275653</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/165837_a3be5a23f46e568a79be83cc477cdcd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F165837_a3be5a23f46e568a79be83cc477cdcd5.jpg&h=57d6a59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活動日期：<br />\n6 月 8 日維護後 至 7 月 13 日維護前 <br />\n<br />\n全新 ★ 5 英雄登場：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">★5 連尼住<br />\n★5 望遠<br />\n★5 六道．仙人<br />\n★5 老衲<br />\n★5 Mr.A</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n六道仙人親臨「戰月勇者」直播<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/292474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/292474</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWac91v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWac91v.png&h=a5b1f4c0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2eaa686abd9063ff3a9b8507f3243ada69e0c1e0","tid":995090,"uid":207369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cd4294c66e5c88523c3767de0646ac00dc1626","tid":995090,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"【戰月勇者x 達哥】 合作活動正式開放這次能夠邀請到香港著名實況主── 達哥，與我們遊戲合作，小編真的感到很開心～ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/160725_7ce164284c6bd5518bd548f1b4fc1e07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F160725_7ce164284c6bd5518bd548f1b4fc1e07.jpg&h=c2947482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/heroesflick/posts/1328139423920697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fheroesflick%2Fposts%2F1328139423920697&d=1JqvwWNHjQPDp8tWt%2FwICi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=aeb90484\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/heroesflick/posts/1328139423920697</a>"},{"pid":"0c0ed6a0d160eea1aaeac61602700734c0dcab1e","tid":995090,"uid":135141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"達哥徒弟美其斤 高匕匕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj